headline: 5 Once-Sleepy Dividend Utility Companies Are Striking Massive Deals With Big Tech
summary: What could be a better avenue than utility stocks that pay dependable, often large, dividend payments every quarter? These five stocks could be perfect for Boomer and Gen X investors.
